{"tid":1982833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿放映會播《鏗鏘集》聲浪大　屠宰員持剁肉刀踩場　認罪獲裁判官香淑嫻判罰款及緩刑","createTime":"2020-04-21T12:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T03:46:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa4eba095992e9f034715e689c4d8bd67e6bb83","tid":1982833,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:14:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%92%AD-%E9%8F%97%E9%8F%98%E9%9B%86-%E8%81%B2%E6%B5%AA%E5%A4%A7-%E5%B1%A0%E5%AE%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8C%81%E5%89%81%E8%82%89%E5%88%80%E8%B8%A9%E5%A0%B4-%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%A4%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE%E5%8F%8A%E7%B7%A9%E5%88%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%2598%25A0%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2592%25AD-%25E9%258F%2597%25E9%258F%2598%25E9%259B%2586-%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%25B5%25AA%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E5%25AE%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2589%2581%25E8%2582%2589%25E5%2588%2580%25E8%25B8%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E5%2588%2591%2F&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiVlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=e97e2624\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%2598%25A0%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2592%25AD-%25E9%258F%2597%25E9%258F%2598%25E9%259B%2586-%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%25B5%25AA%25E5%25A4%25A7-%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E5%25AE%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258C%2581%25E5%2589%2581%25E8%2582%2589%25E5%2588%2580%25E8%25B8%25A9%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%258F%258A%25E7%25B7%25A9%25E5%2588%2591%2F&h=bb12c86d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%92%AD-%E9%8F%97%E9%8F%98%E9%9B%86-%E8%81%B2%E6%B5%AA%E5%A4%A7-%E5%B1%A0%E5%AE%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8C%81%E5%89%81%E8%82%89%E5%88%80%E8%B8%A9%E5%A0%B4-%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%A4%E7%BD%B0%E6%AC%BE%E5%8F%8A%E7%B7%A9%E5%88%91/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>去年8月14日有人於西營盤舉辦小型放映會播放《鏗鏘集》等影片，期間一名報稱為屠宰員的31歲男子，手持剁肉刀現身指責聲浪過大，更一度情緒激動踢打擴音器，要求停止播放。其後有人報警，屠宰員被捕。他今於東區裁判法院承認刑事毀壞及管有攻擊性武器兩罪，裁判官香淑嫻判他罰款3,000元，入獄2個月、緩刑18個月，另須賠償事主1,000元。</strong><br />\n<br />\n被告郭毅（31歲，報稱屠宰員）原被控刑毀及在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪，控方其後將後者改為管有攻擊性武器罪，指他於去年8月14日，於西營盤水街東利大廈外，無合理辯解而損壞屬於黃永志的擴音器；及於同日同地，無合理權限或合理辯解而管有攻擊性武器，即一把剁肉刀。<br />\n<br />\n案情透露，被告當晚約9時現身涉事的放映會，表示自己是東利大廈的住戶，受到放映會影片的聲浪滋擾，要求調低聲量。事主黃永志隨即照做，但未幾被告手持一把剁肉刀再次出現，稱仍受到聲浪滋擾，且情緒激動地要求黃停止放映會，並用腳踢打擴音器。當時現場有約15人目擊事件，及有人拍攝案發經過。其後有人報警，被告被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同一個官，隔住口罩咬就會要拉佢坐監，呢單出埋刀就判緩刑</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0614efdfc201a1ecce191ad028e057934ceeb344","tid":1982833,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f62464d8ed7aeeb4762c0151e8ccaca591a87bb","tid":1982833,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:19:28.000Z","msg":"法官:<br />\n<br />\n你係黑社會? 我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b364b0b566be568fc5d1e7242b9b6c0f032b742d","tid":1982833,"uid":104684,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:20:47.000Z","msg":"放香淑嫻入制裁名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢d仔女唔洗去美國，永享支那榮耀"},{"pid":"f3b8e5513b96c5c1ce4eb517bd378775a32db4b7","tid":1982833,"uid":315761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:22:01.000Z","msg":"over my dead body<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse